{"tid":1502624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬鞍山－烏溪沙巴士站連儂牆上線了","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:09:58.000Z","uid":33875,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ef31c775b943f546ea173c229b8e06daeed6a5","tid":1502624,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4ebVcnYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4ebVcnYh.png&h=851c0d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日講開樓下幅牆好單調 ，問下有冇人想佈置下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幅牆前後大概有八、九張文宣出現過<br />\n右邊幾張太高藍老膝頭痛跳唔到上去撕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hWWc5TGCl2Y&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhWWc5TGCl2Y%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84vYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=6b1a3384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hWWc5TGCl2Y&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n人鏈完返去開咗個頭，寫咗幾隻字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">823 烏溪沙連儂牆正式上線</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過第二朝就唔見哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/76V9NtSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F76V9NtSh.png&h=baa7a41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估唔到824 下午有兩位女學生山長水遠由新西騎牛牛到新東搞撕一貼十 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮無錢派，唯有應承請佢飲汽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">824 烏溪沙連儂牆又上線喇</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/luuMnBXh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FluuMnBXh.png&h=9fce4a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利安、翠擁、銀湖、迎海既手足係時候準備紙筆墨硯了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fea353681036818a32e059eba4749a87fc6437","tid":1502624,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"陳帆呼籲市民：寧願參加其他活動都好過堵塞機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1498684</a>"},{"pid":"4bb99756907f074f833a7c79dd8a16c975ac110d","tid":1502624,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jJoyp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jJoyp3.jpg&h=dac303d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排隊印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485c8f7be70fbe8c807548f01ca48962487cb5b2","tid":1502624,"uid":51626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"自製漿糊中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c8183544b3b6cd13a8284275b993eb6aa5812","tid":1502624,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"連狗連豬Pepe嘅畫,meme,sticker<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1499549/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1499549/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/qc9zfQ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqc9zfQ7.png&h=ebbb8eb